    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A little boy didn’t listen to his mother’s warnings that eating too much at night would cause nightmares. Now, he must face hordes of monsters and defeat the nightmare bosses to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The demo version of Deep Deep Deep Nightmare offers a preview of what’s to come in the full game, allowing you to face challenging hordes of monsters, defeat bosses, and experiment with a variety of weapons and spells. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEMO FEATURES</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This demo includes 1 tutorial level and 2 campaign levels. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 weapons to equip your arsenal </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 spells to equip your arsenal </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 boss fights </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller support</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEFEAT THE NIGHTMARE BOSSES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face mini-bosses and nightmare bosses. Use your weapons and skills to win each battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284850/extras/cfb2a78edba930df41dbe1733964579d.poster.avif?t=1728923584\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284850/extras/cfb2a78edba930df41dbe1733964579d.webm?t=1728923584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284850/extras/cfb2a78edba930df41dbe1733964579d.mp4?t=1728923584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE THE HORDES OF MONSTERS AND TRAPS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Withstand waves of monsters and deadly traps. Test your skills in increasingly difficult levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284850/extras/729d59d7b829b74e1f51c69959e3c1a3.poster.avif?t=1728923584\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284850/extras/729d59d7b829b74e1f51c69959e3c1a3.webm?t=1728923584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284850/extras/729d59d7b829b74e1f51c69959e3c1a3.mp4?t=1728923584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR ARSENAL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your arsenal with a variety of weapons and spells. Personalize your strategy and always be ready for the next enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284850/extras/0c8e79179c6920ca34a265abc1c2a867.poster.avif?t=1728923584\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284850/extras/0c8e79179c6920ca34a265abc1c2a867.webm?t=1728923584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284850/extras/0c8e79179c6920ca34a265abc1c2a867.mp4?t=1728923584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
